{"tid":416792,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你係2007/2008年高位入市既話........今日會.......","createTime":"2017-09-28T05:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T10:17:41.000Z","uid":132198,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"019c9d1b5fe81a3ea14a7ee3e58a201e96da0f45","tid":416792,"uid":132198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T05:37:16.000Z","msg":"啱先係Bloomberg見到篇文話如果你係2007/2008頂位入市(入S&amp;P 500 Index)既話 你會係5年回本 10年後既今日差唔多Double (講緊Total Returns 所以計埋息Reinvested)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iwYwoq4.11tY/v2/1000x-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.bwbx.io%2Fimages%2Fusers%2FiqjWHBFdfxIU%2FiwYwoq4.11tY%2Fv2%2F1000x-1.png&h=71f49e9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-09-26/doubling-your-money-in-stocks-by-buying-at-peak-of-a-bull-market\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2017-09-26%2Fdoubling-your-money-in-stocks-by-buying-at-peak-of-a-bull-market&d=iSYwik3gVh0G1Y9y2f78fdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=61aed06c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-09-26/doubling-your-money-in-stocks-by-buying-at-peak-of-a-bull-market</a><br />\n<br />\n所以我又好奇想睇下如果買盈富2800會點...<br />\n(因為數據關係 我只能當係2008年頭 2007年尾 入市, 搵唔到準確高位入市, 真正既高位都係接近2007年尾)<br />\n<br />\n結果:<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/132821_d8c12f25d98ff725a7792b29a4bfedcc.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F132821_d8c12f25d98ff725a7792b29a4bfedcc.PNG&h=2e728d1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(Data from 盈富官網 個表就我自己整)<br />\n你會係2013年底回本(多美市一年回本)  至今只係升左36% 遠少於美市<br />\n<br />\n結論:<br />\n1. 睇得夠長線同長揸既話 金融海嘯都唔怕<br />\n2. 唔好淨係買港市, 你識既話, 入多幾個市分散風險, 港市始終唔夠穩, 應主力美市 (再講多次 如果你識得既話, 唔識可以花D時間研究, 唔識又亂黎既話 可能衰多兩錢重)"},{"pid":"8a68e27e55e3fdbffd339b3307eb15e9ea97e5fc","tid":416792,"uid":65479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:07:32.000Z","msg":"美股成熟好多<br />\n港股未必做到"},{"pid":"7d841c51de2481e7576af98ee87bcb9bee266c2b","tid":416792,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:11:10.000Z","msg":"剩係美元資產已經夠屈<br />\n港元應該會被脫Out"},{"pid":"cf0119b7348da5e53a7b5e345014dc8123947a33","tid":416792,"uid":62067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T10:57:15.000Z","msg":"邊度買美股平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216e82a41e4d5cbcb1f9231d8f2c2988cde7cfa3","tid":416792,"uid":124282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T11:00:31.000Z","msg":"股息有無計？盈富1年都2-3%"},{"pid":"8bdd45b30847780eceaefccca8c0af85f76d8ab2","tid":416792,"uid":132198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T18:03:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>股息有無計？盈富1年都2-3%</blockquote><br />\n計左 唔計既話6年都回唔到本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc7a7a0131f73bf6ed7d7aff99e121036e07268","tid":416792,"uid":126329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T00:40:34.000Z","msg":"你睇下日本經濟泡沫爆前d股市數據先啦<br />\nview back真係多鳩餘 你係醒就係08年買<br />\n以家係黎做勝利宣言"},{"pid":"101d5bbd6435f3dee5a2ef07ac6f0b5a5de48216","tid":416792,"uid":126329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T00:41:23.000Z","msg":"我都識講啦 03 年買騰訊 跑撚贏好多美股tim"},{"pid":"26f72e2b6f4baa752ca7575ee5b1e9f32adb555c","tid":416792,"uid":62067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T10:10:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都識講啦 03 年買騰訊 跑撚贏好多美股tim</blockquote><br />\n03騰訊都未上市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcc9e6f9888f01b407c1c2cdd36e561f64339245","tid":416792,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,